eets or exceeds all job requirements.\\n\\nRecommendation: Strongly Recommend extending an offer for the Data Scientist position.\\n\\n------------------------------------------------------------\\nEnd of Report\\n------------------------------------------------------------\\n```\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-28T12:33:09.863268\"\n}"}
